                <small>Last reviewed: <time datetime="#">29/07/2016 09:02 AM</time></small>
</header>


<p><strong>Thames Water is committed to protecting your privacy and complying with the Data Protection Act 1998.</strong></p>
<p>This policy sets out the basis on which we collect, use and disclose your personal data, as well as your rights in respect of such personal data.  </p>
<p>In this privacy policy references to "we", "us" and &ldquo;our&rdquo; are to Thames Water Ltd, Thames Water Utilities Ltd, Thames Water Commercial Services Ltd and all parent and subsidiary companies of those companies (also referred to as the &ldquo;Thames Group&rdquo;).</p>
<p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time and will state on the policy the date when the policy was last updated.</p>
